cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with 3D hand and body pose estimation from depth images. It may also belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as pose estimation is a crucial task in robotics. The use of anchor points and regression networks suggests that it may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the mention of ResNet-50 as the backbone network suggests that it may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
